Jimena Sánchez (born Jimena Sánchez Mejía Reyes; Mexico City; September 28, 1984)12 is a Mexican sports journalist, model and actress who currently works for Fox Sports Latin America and Fox Deportes. She is known for hosting the shows The Best of Fox Sports and WWE Saturday Night.

I don't know if most of you know it but the truth is that since I started dating as a sports commentator I always liked it, I hope you like it too.
